sed sub-connected active RIS can\nsignificantly reduce the hardware cost and power consumption, and achieve great\nperformance improvement when power budget at RIS is limited.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2022 07:04:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-06"}
