e conclude that MInIT can help DNS by\nproperly capturing small-scale turbulent stresses which has potential\nimplications on the dynamics of highly-magnetized rotating compact objects,\nsuch as those formed during binary neutron star mergers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2022 12:02:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-26"}
